org.appkit.registry
Class Images

java.lang.Object
  org.appkit.registry.Images

public final class Images
extends Object

SWT Image cache/registry
Creates, assigns and caches Images. Images can be set on a Buttons, Labels, Shells or an Control for which an Images.ImageInterface is added. Use of an image is deregistered when the widget is disposed, if a different Images is set via this registry or manually via the putBack(Widget) method.
This uses a simple counter to keep of track of usage. If it drops to 0, the image is disposed.
The methods expect Suppliers for keys. These can be easily implemented by an Enum for example.
